INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (157001, 'This savoring of life is no small thing. The element of wonder is almost lost today with the onslaught of the media and gadgets of our noisy world. To let a child lose it is to make him blind and deaf to the best of life.', 677, 0), (157002, 'I live life in the light.', 2878, 0), (157003, 'No one will live forever.', 2878, 0), (157004, 'Living the life I wanted was my ultimate responsibility. Learning to forgive was my ultimate act of self-love.', 23385, 0), (157005, 'Belief and faith are great, but very few people have been led astray by thinking for themselves.', 3299, 0), (157006, 'You never live an inch without involvement and hurting people and fucking yourself everlastingly.', 4331, 0), (157007, 'When you first meet a person, sometimes they''ll pretend to be all that you like. Deception is hard to predict instantly at times, but if you hang with them for a while their true colors will eventually begin to show.', 3145, 0), (157008, 'What have I to prove, and to whom, and why? I''m keen enough to want nothing more than to live a simple, humble, unfettered life.', 3711, 0), (157009, 'Life is but a sleep disturbed By dreaming', 81, 0), (157010, 'Maturity is when you stop complaining and making excuses and start making changes.', 3604, 0), (157011, 'It is important to know you are not above or below anyone.', 9273, 0), (157012, 'We only regret the chances we didn''t take', 24469, 0), (157013, 'A life well lived is better than too many quotesSometimes we are too fast, we want to shoot at people with our knowledge of the Bible. We don''t really need to open our mouth much! Like the bible says: we are suppose to be those living epistles read of all men. Our actions talk more than our religious behaviour. Let''s be more showing Christ than showing our knowledge about the Word. God bless you.', 19279, 0), (157014, 'Like taking a breath, learning was the simple and extraordinary result of being alive.', 